*'''''Crossfire'' 02A Explorer''' (2010)
  +
:An unlicensed transforming figure and accessory upgrade kit by [[FansProject]] for the ''Universe''/''Revenge of the Fallen'' Bruticus Maximus combiner set. The "Explorer" figure is a modern redesign of Blast Off, which also transforms into a space shuttle. The tail fin transforms into the figure's ax and unfolds to become a sword for Bruticus. Other accessories in the package include a pair of missile launchers (which double as Bruticus' new shoulder joints), a redesigned foot for Bruticus and a cannon for Onslaught.<ref>[http://www.tfw2005.com/transformers-news/universe-classics-20-29/images-of-fansproject-crossfire-sets-combined-form-and-weapons-169120/ TFW2005.com - Images of FansProject Crossfire Sets, Combined Form and Weapons]</ref>
